                                <span class="step-description">
                        There are two ways of using a function in your html code:<br>
                        <h2>Importing the basic script</h2>
                        <p>
                            To do this, you just need to add a script tag to your html similar to this one:
                            <br>
                            &ltscript type="text/javascript" src="http://localhost:3000/basic_import"&gt&lt/script&gt
                            <br>
                        </p>
                        <h2>Importing the function directly</h2>
                        <p>
                            To import a function directly, just add it as a script in your html code like this:
                            <br>
                            &ltscript type="text/javascript" src="http://localhost:3000/fn-02"&gt&lt/script&gt
                            <br>
                            Where fn-02 is the function id, which can be seen in the Function Details page of every function.
                        </p>
